# =============================================================================
# DATABASE CONFIGURATION
# =============================================================================
# 
# Choose ONE of the following setups:
#
# OPTION 1: Local Docker PostgreSQL (recommended for development)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Start the container: docker compose up -d
# 2. Use this connection string:
#
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://skriuw:skriuw_dev@localhost:5432/skriuw
# DATABASE_PROVIDER=postgres
#
# OPTION 2: Neon Cloud (for production or cloud development)
# -----------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Get your connection string from https://console.neon.tech
# 2. Use this format:
#
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@ep-xxxx.region.aws.neon.tech/dbname?sslmode=require
# DATABASE_PROVIDER=neon
#
# =============================================================================

# Uncomment ONE of these configurations:

# --- LOCAL DOCKER (recommended for dev) ---
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://skriuw:skriuw_dev@localhost:5432/skriuw
# DATABASE_PROVIDER=postgres

# --- NEON CLOUD ---
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://neondb_owner:xxx@ep-xxx.region.aws.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require
# DATABASE_PROVIDER=neon
